EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
MOROCCO.
DNC 01, DNC 08.
1. GUNNERY EXERCISES:
   A. 03 MAR IN AREA WITHIN
      20 MILES OF 29-53N 010-15W
      BETWEEN 270 DEGREES AND 360 DEGREES.
   B. 04 AND 05 MAR IN AREA BOUND BY
      29-08N 011-28W, 29-18N 011-06W,
      28-46N 010-48W, 28-42N 010-56W.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 06 MAR 21.
